Use 1 array to mark all inputable actors that won't input actions automatically
Use BattleManager._actionBattlers to mark all Action Execution Subjects
Change notification notetags for abstract notetag readers reading many notetags should mark which data type(actor, class, equip, 
enemy, state) might be changed, so the abstract notetag readers might not have to reread everything, as partial results for each
data type are cached as well(not just the final result that's actually used)
